flowchart TB
    START([MULAI]) --> HOME[Halaman Dashboard]
    HOME --> NH[Halaman Nutrisi Harian]

    NH --> SYNC[Sync Sekarang]

    SYNC --> CHECK{Cek Data}
    CHECK -->|Data Sudah Ada| DONE1([Tidak Ada Perubahan])
    CHECK -->|Belum Ada| WINDOW[Ambil 7 Data Terakhir]

    WINDOW --> FLASK[Kirim ke Flask API]
    FLASK --> LSTM[LSTM Prediksi]
    LSTM --> HASIL[Hasil Prediksi]
    HASIL --> SIMPAN[Simpan ke Database]
    SIMPAN --> DONE2([Selesai])

    DONE1 -.-> HOME
    DONE2 -.-> HOME

    style START fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#2E7D32,color:#fff
    style HOME fill:#2196F3,stroke:#1565C0,color:#fff
    style NH fill:#9C27B0,stroke:#6A1B9A,color:#fff
    style LSTM fill:#FF9800,stroke:#E65100,color:#fff
    style DONE1 fill:#9E9E9E,stroke:#616161,color:#fff
    style DONE2 fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#2E7D32,color:#fff